{115}{}{我为莱特先生工作，管理他在铀城的生意。但是在人和牲畜开始消失后，所有的工人都离开了，所以莱特生气了，把我卖了做奴隶。[他悲伤地耸耸肩]雷诺就是这样。前一分钟你是个成功的人，然后。。。 -- I worked for Mr. Wright, managing his business in Uranium City. But all the workers took off after people and livestock started to disappear, so Wright got angry and sold me into slavery. [he shrugs sadly] That's how it works in Reno. One minute you're a made man, and then...}
