#{123}{}{Really?! Oh, Marilyn... Damn, she's really something. Can't say I'm surprised. But... See this collar? If I try to escape, it'll kill me. And if I do escape, they'll find me - and then I'll wish it had killed me! The only way I'm getting out of here is if Luciano agrees. Will... Will you help me? For Uranium City? And... For Marilyn?}
{123}{}{真正地？！哦，玛丽莲。。。妈的，她真了不起。不能说我很惊讶。但是。。。看到这个领子了吗？如果我想逃跑，它会杀了我的。如果我真的逃跑了，他们会找到我的-然后我会希望它杀了我！如果卢西亚诺同意，我就离开这里。威尔。。。你能帮我吗？为了铀城？还有。。。为了玛丽莲？ -- Really?! Oh, Marilyn... Damn, she's really something. Can't say I'm surprised. But... See this collar? If I try to escape, it'll kill me. And if I do escape, they'll find me - and then I'll wish it had killed me! The only way I'm getting out of here is if Luciano agrees. Will... Will you help me? For Uranium City? And... For Marilyn?}
