{131}{}{哦。。。可以。。。听起来，呃，不错，除了到处都是武装保安和我的一万伏特项链。你记得这些，对吧？ -- Oh... Okay... That sounds, uh, great, except for the armed security all over the place and my ten-thousand-volt necklace. You do remember all that, right?}
